A person, firm, partner in a firm, corporation, or a shareholder in an S corporation doing business in the state of Missouri and subject to the state income tax imposed in
chapter 143
;

A corporation subject to the annual corporation franchise tax imposed in
chapter 147
;

Any other financial institution paying taxes to the state of Missouri or any political subdivision of this state under
chapter 148
;

An individual subject to the state income tax imposed in
chapter 143
;
